THIRD-PARTY MATERIAL (NOT REPRODUCED)
-------------------------------------
The BoK names and applies third-party industry and consensus standards that remain the
copyright of their respective publishers, including (non-exhaustive): SAE/AS6500,
AS9100, AS9102, AS9103, AS9145, AS5553, AS6174; ISO 9001; IEEE 15288.1 and 15288.2;
and MIL-STD-881. This pack does NOT reproduce the text of those standards. It cites
them by designation and describes, in original wording, how the BoK directs them to be
used. For normative requirements, consult the standards themselves from their
publishers (SAE International, ISO, IEEE).

